Office Space;;93;;80;;R;;Corporate drone Peter Gibbons (Ron Livingston) hates his soul-killing job at software company Initech. While undergoing hypnotherapy, Peter is left in a blissful state when his therapist dies in the middle of their session. He refuses to work overtime, plays games at his desk and unintentionally charms two consultants into putting him on the management fast-track. When Peter's friends learn they're about to be downsized, they hatch a revenge plot against the company inspired by "Superman III.";;Comedy;;Mike Judge;;1999;;Ron Livingston,Jennifer Aniston,David Herman,Ajay Naidu,Diedrich Bader,Stephen Root,Gary Cole,Richard Riehle,John C. McGinley,Ali Wentworth,Rupert Reyes,Todd Duffey,Jennifer Emerson;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/office_space